Package javelin.model.world.location.town.labor.productive

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Deforestate
    Converts a forest tile in the district into 50% extra labor (automatically adds a Growth project if there isn't another project to benefit from this).
    Mine
    Found only on Mountains, mines allow a Squad to mine gold over a period of time or leave Combatants there for long-term mining - in which case the resulting gold needs to be gathered there by a Squad later on.
